 72	 * `routeFormAction` (the same wrapper the hand-tuned forms use), so a migrated
 73	 * route is `export const action = formAction({ form, notify, success })` — no
 74	 * inline pipeline. The body yields a {@link FormSuccess} only to satisfy the
 75	 * wrapper's body type; on the happy path the terminal `toast.redirect` fails with
 76	 * a `RedirectError` the wrapper forwards to the runtime, so the return is
 77	 * unreachable on success.
